cinnamon.engine.utils

Class BinaryBVHTestSuite

  • java.lang.Object
    • cinnamon.engine.utils.BinaryBVHTestSuite

  • public class BinaryBVHTestSuite
extends Object

    Defines the test subject class BoxPartitionable, input set generation, and its parameters. Executing this test suite will run the tests in BinaryBVHTest and BinaryBVHPropertyTest.
